cross the full AI lifecycle resonates strongly with my approach to engineering.\n\nI’m particularly drawn to the engineering culture described as clean code, experimentation,\ncollaboration, and shipping real products rather than demos. That environment aligns closely\nwith how I prefer to work and grow.\n\nI’ve attached my resume, and here’s my GitHub profile for your reference.\n\nThank you for your time and consideration.', 'language': None, 'chunk_index': 2}]
